IMAPAccount protonmail
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User anton@tetov.se
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup protonmail_user anton@tetov.se"
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
SSLType STARTTLS
CertificateFile ~/.config/protonmail/bridge/cert.pem

IMAPStore protonmail-remote
Account protonmail

MaildirStore protonmail-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/protonmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/protonmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel protonmail
Far :protonmail-remote:
Near :protonmail-local:
Patterns * !"All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount lth
Host imap.lu.se
Port 993
User an6802jo@lu.se
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup org LTH imap_user an6802jo@lu.se"
SSLType IMAPS
# SSLVersion TLSv1.2

IMAPStore lth-remote
Account lth

MaildirStore lth-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/lth/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/lth/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel lth-often
Far :lth-remote:
Near :lth-local:
Patterns INBOX Drafts "Sent Items" "Deleted Items" "Junk Email"
Create Both
SyncState *

Channel lth-less-often
Far :lth-remote:
Near :lth-local:
Patterns Archive "dirs/*"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group lth-all
Channel lth-often
Channel lth-less-often
